org.modelio.metamodel.uml.statik

Interface Operation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BehavioralFeature, java.lang.Comparable<MObject>, Element, Feature, MObject, ModelElement, UmlModelElement

    public interface Operation
extends BehavioralFeature
    Operation v0.0.9054 In Modelio, this metaclass defines both the Operation, and the method implementing it. An Operation belongs to its Classifier.
